@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
    ViewBag.Title = "Grower Stories – Drip Smart USA";
}

<section class="page-hero" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0e1438 0%, #181F4E 100%);position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464226184884-fa280b87c399?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;opacity:0.18;pointer-events:none;"></div>
    <div class="container page-hero-inner" style="position:relative;">
        <div class="page-hero-text">
            <nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>Grower Stories</span></nav>
            <h1>Real Farmers.<br/>Real Results.</h1>
            <p>Every farm is different. These are the stories of growers who faced real challenges — water scarcity, poor soils, extreme weather — and found a way forward with precision irrigation.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Stories Grid -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="stories-grid">
            <article class="story-card">
                <div class="story-card-header">
                    <div class="story-avatar">WP</div>
                    <div><div class="story-name">William K. Perry</div><div class="story-meta">Alfalfa · Tonopah, Arizona</div></div>
                    <div class="story-badge">Case Study</div>
                </div>
                <h3>"We turned Arizona's toughest water restrictions into our competitive advantage."</h3>
                <p>By switching to SDI, William K. Perry Farms dramatically improved water efficiency while maintaining high alfalfa yields — even as neighboring farms struggled with water scarcity.</p>
                <div class="story-results">
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">48%</span><span>Water Savings</span></div>
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">+22%</span><span>Yield Increase</span></div>
                </div>
                <a href="/growers-stories/william-perry" class="story-link">Read Full Story →</a>
            </article>

            <article class="story-card">
                <div class="story-card-header">
                    <div class="story-avatar" style="background:#0288d1">KM</div>
                    <div><div class="story-name">Kevin Matthews</div><div class="story-meta">Soybeans · North Carolina</div></div>
                    <div class="story-badge">Case Study</div>
                </div>
                <h3>"My worst-producing ground became my best-producing ground in one season."</h3>
                <p>Kevin was ready to write off his low-yielding fields. After installing drip with targeted fertigation, those same fields outperformed his irrigated acreage — despite a record drought year.</p>
                <div class="story-results">
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">+35%</span><span>Yield Increase</span></div>
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">$18K</span><span>Cost Savings/yr</span></div>
                </div>
                <a href="/growers-stories/kevin-matthews" class="story-link">Read Full Story →</a>
            </article>

            <article class="story-card">
                <div class="story-card-header">
                    <div class="story-avatar" style="background:#f57c00">TC</div>
                    <div><div class="story-name">Tony Cox</div><div class="story-meta">Cotton · West Texas</div></div>
                    <div class="story-badge">Case Study</div>
                </div>
                <h3>"When our groundwater turned salty, drip irrigation saved the farm."</h3>
                <p>Faced with rising salinity in his groundwater, Tony used subsurface drip to manage salt accumulation — keeping his cotton operation viable when conventional systems would have failed.</p>
                <div class="story-results">
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">Farm</span><span>Saved</span></div>
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">3 yrs</span><span>ROI Achieved</span></div>
                </div>
                <a href="/growers-stories/tony-cox" class="story-link">Read Full Story →</a>
            </article>

            <article class="story-card">
                <div class="story-card-header">
                    <div class="story-avatar" style="background:#388e3c">AS</div>
                    <div><div class="story-name">Arrowhead Seed Co.</div><div class="story-meta">Hemp · South Carolina</div></div>
                    <div class="story-badge">Case Study</div>
                </div>
                <h3>"Being first to market with feminized hemp seed required a system we could trust."</h3>
                <p>As one of the first licensed hemp operations in South Carolina, Arrowhead needed irrigation that could handle a sensitive, high-value crop with zero margin for error.</p>
                <div class="story-results">
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">1st</span><span>In State</span></div>
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">100%</span><span>System Uptime</span></div>
                </div>
                <a href="/growers-stories/arrowhead-seed" class="story-link">Read Full Story →</a>
            </article>

            <article class="story-card">
                <div class="story-card-header">
                    <div class="story-avatar" style="background:#7b1fa2">ML</div>
                    <div><div class="story-name">Maria Lopez</div><div class="story-meta">Almonds · Fresno, California</div></div>
                    <div class="story-badge">Testimonial</div>
                </div>
                <h3>"Managing 3,000 acres from my kitchen table changed everything."</h3>
                <p>After installing DripSphere OS™ across her almond operation, Maria cut labor costs and improved irrigation uniformity across all her blocks — with full visibility on her phone.</p>
                <div class="story-results">
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">3,000</span><span>Acres Managed</span></div>
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">-30%</span><span>Labor Cost</span></div>
                </div>
                <a href="/growers-stories/maria-lopez" class="story-link">Read Full Story →</a>
            </article>

            <article class="story-card">
                <div class="story-card-header">
                    <div class="story-avatar" style="background:#c62828">JR</div>
                    <div><div class="story-name">Jim Reynolds</div><div class="story-meta">Strawberries · Watsonville, CA</div></div>
                    <div class="story-badge">Testimonial</div>
                </div>
                <h3>"Paid for itself in two seasons. Best investment we've made in 20 years."</h3>
                <p>Jim's strawberry operation saw water bills drop by nearly half, while fruit quality reached an all-time high — thanks to consistent soil moisture throughout every growth stage.</p>
                <div class="story-results">
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">47%</span><span>Water Bill Drop</span></div>
                    <div class="story-result"><span class="result-num">2 yrs</span><span>Full ROI</span></div>
                </div>
                <a href="/growers-stories/jim-reynolds" class="story-link">Read Full Story →</a>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- PHOTO BAND -->
<div style="width:100%;height:380px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464226184884-fa280b87c399?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80" alt="Farmer examining crops in irrigated field" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 45%;" />
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to right, rgba(14,20,56,0.82) 0%, rgba(14,20,56,0.12) 68%);display:flex;align-items:center;">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="max-width:540px;color:white;">
                <div style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#89C1FF;margin-bottom:10px;">10,000+ Growers Served</div>
                <div style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.25;margin-bottom:14px;">Every farm has a story.<br>We help write better ones.</div>
                <p style="opacity:0.85;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.6;">From 40-acre family operations to 10,000-acre commercial farms — DripSmart growers consistently out-yield their neighbors and under-use their water.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- CTA -->
